title: GoPro: James Stewart's Winning Run -  2015 Red Bull Straight Rhythm at Pomona
description:
Ride along with James Stewart as he captures his second consecutive Red Bull Straight Rhythm win in the Open Class at the Fairplex in Pomona, California.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera
